        {
          "text": "Melody – Combining Notes from a Scale"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "In the simplest terms, a melody is just taking the notes from a scale and arranging them in different ways."
        }
      ]
