    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Notice that we didn’t change any pitches—only the timing of each note. This timing layout is what we call “rhythm.”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
