    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Whenever you craft a nice melody or hear one, consciously record and review it—voice memos, DAWs(like garageband、guitar pro)."
        },
        {
          "text": "Keep accumulating, and you’ll build an internal melody library."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
