        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "In short, melody relies heavily on taste and vocabulary. Pay attention to the melodies that move you in daily life. But melody alone isn’t enough for a song—it’s too bare. We still need “accompaniment.” Next, let’s enter the world of "
